CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 23, 1946, pg. 17, reads: "Going Up! - These smiles denote satisfaction as executives of The Pittsburgh Courier look at the 300,000th copy of The Courier which rolled off the press last week..."
TitMainTitle: Head pressman Bud Waters operating press in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper printing plant, with others including Jessie Vann, and Bill Nunn Sr. wearing three piece suit, standing behind him
